                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-142-victim1476 t18210411-142-viclabel873"></join>, and live at the corner of <placeName id="t18210411-142-crimeloc874">Skinner-street, Somers-town</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18210411-142-crimeloc874" type="placeName" value="Skinner-street, Somers-town"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18210411-142-crimeloc874" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-142-off871 t18210411-142-crimeloc874"></join>. On Saturday afternoon, the 31st of March, I was in my back parlour; a person said a man had stolen some meat. I ran out and overtook the prisoner six doors off, and found the beef and pork on him; he said he meant to pay for it - he was rescued, and my son followed him over the fields, and secured him.</p>
